<BaseLayout title="Brownian Crystallisation">
  <h1>Brownian Crystallisation (Diffusion-Limited Aggregation)</h1>

  <p class="project-subtitle">
    Stochastic simulation of crystallisation via Brownian motion and irreversible aggregation.
  </p>

  <img
    src="/images/crystallisation.gif"
